  "detailed_description": "<strong>Survivor Challenge TD</strong> - is a Tower Defense game where you manage a single tower and add upgrades to it. Buy abilities, enhance upgrades, and defeat the boss!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2443170/extras/ff9a1d08d25743ce1e6d1b229188661d.poster.avif?t=1764900775\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2443170/extras/ff9a1d08d25743ce1e6d1b229188661d.webm?t=1764900775\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2443170/extras/ff9a1d08d25743ce1e6d1b229188661d.mp4?t=1764900775\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Defeat the Enemies</h2>Hold out until the boss arrives and defeat him to complete the level!<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Buy abilities to attack enemies<br></li><li> Combine elements to gain maximum power<br></li><li> Find successful combos and builds<br></li><li> Complete levels to unlock new abilities</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Elemental Variants</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2443170/extras/5b02716647372edc763eaa9e4974d86a.poster.avif?t=1764900775\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2443170/extras/5b02716647372edc763eaa9e4974d86a.webm?t=1764900775\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2443170/extras/5b02716647372edc763eaa9e4974d86a.mp4?t=1764900775\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
